# The image build only needs Cargo.toml, Cargo.lock, and src/ (it runs
# `cargo build --release --bin datamk`). Everything else is excluded so edits to
# tests/docs/config don't invalidate the `COPY . .` layer or bloat the context —
# notably the kind e2e harness under test/, which changes often but never affects
# the binary.
target/
.git/
test/
docs/
.claude/
*.md
